<header class="meta-data--container">
<div class="meta-data--item desktop-only">
<div class="meta-data--icon icon blog-icon engineering"></div>
<a class="category" href="/blog/category/engineering">Engineering</a>
</div>
<div class="meta-data--item">
<img class="meta-data--icon" src="https://gravatar.com/avatar/fba3a14df3e58e399e1452058ebf8fcd?s=20&amp;d=mm" />
<span class="author">Graeme Rocher</span>
</div>
<div class="meta-data--item">
<div class="meta-data--icon icon blog-icon calendar"></div>
<time class="date" pubdate="" datetime="2011-02-15 11:08:00.0">February 15, 2011</time>
</div>
<div class="meta-data--item">
<div class="meta-data--icon icon blog-icon comments"></div>
<a class="comments" data-disqus-identifier="394" href="/blog/2011/02/15/gorm-for-mongodb-new-milestone-richer-experience#disqus_thread">
