<div class="meta-data--icon icon blog-icon comments"></div>
<a class="comments" data-disqus-identifier="599" href="/blog/2011/02/14/springone-2gx-2010-tech-talk-configuration-enhancements-in-spring-3-1#disqus_thread">
</a></div>
</header>
<section class="blog--post desktop-only">
<div><p> </p>
<div style="float: right; width:314px; padding: 10px">
<a href="http://www.infoq.com/presentations/Configuration-in-Spring-3-1"><img height="215" alt="SpringOne 2GX 2010 Tech Talk: Configuration Enhancements in Spring 3.1" width="314" border="0" src="/files/SpringOne2GX2010ChrisBeams.png"></a>
