<a href="http://blog.springsource.com/author/cbeams/">Chris Beams</a>
<p></p>
<p>Also last week <a href="http://blog.springsource.com/author/juergenh/">Juergen Hoeller</a> gave a webinar on the Spring 3.1 milestone release. In case you can were not able to attend in person, a full <a href="http://www.springsource.com/webinar/introducing-spring-framework-31">recording of the webinar</a> has now been posted so you can get all of the details from the source! </p>
